PortSystem 1.0
name		wmmemmon
version		1.0.0
categories	sysutils x11
maintainers	landonf@opendarwin.org
description	An "lcd" dockapp that displays the current memory/swap usage
homepage	http://www.sh.rim.or.jp/~ssato/dockapp/	

long_description WMMemMon is a program to monitor memory/swap usage. \
It is a dockapp that is supported by X window managers such as \
WindowMaker, AfterStep, BlackBox, and Enlightenment.

platforms	darwin freebsd
master_sites	http://www.sh.rim.or.jp/~ssato/src/
checksums	md5 b966aebfbf61763a075691aae366dc3f

depends_build   lib:libX11.6:XFree86
